" Mappings
" ########

" ------------------------------

" Remap `jk` to escape (to exit the Insert mode quickly).
inoremap jk <ESC>

" Change up/down to move one visual line at a time instead of one line text.
nnoremap j gj
nnoremap k gk

" ------------------------------

" Disable arrows.
nnoremap <up> <nop>
nnoremap <down> <nop>
nnoremap <left> <nop>
nnoremap <right> <nop>
inoremap <up> <nop>
inoremap <down> <nop>
inoremap <left> <nop>
inoremap <right> <nop>
